    "description": {
      "gm": "",
      "value": "<p><strong>Activate</strong> <span class=\"action-glyph\">A</span> Interact</p>\n<hr />\n<p>Your features become striking and your voice becomes musical and commanding, though facts and figures become hazy for you and emotion clouds your ability to reason.</p>\n<p><strong>Benefit</strong> You gain a +3 item bonus to Deception, Diplomacy, Intimidation and Performance checks. Your critical failures with any of these skills become failures instead.</p>\n<p><strong>Drawback</strong> You take a -2 item penalty to Arcana, Crafting, Lore, Occultism, and Society checks. Choose one skill in which you are trained; for the duration, you become untrained in that skill. All your failures to @UUID[Compendium.pf2e.actionspf2e.Item.1OagaWtBpVXExToo]{Recall Knowledge} become critical failures.</p>\n<p><strong>Duration</strong> 1 hour.</p>\n<p>@UUID[Compendium.pf2e.equipment-effects.Item.oAewXfq9c0ecaSfw]{Effect: Silvertongue Mutagen (Greater)}</p>"
